properties.areaDesc: Port Washington to North Point Light WI; Sheboygan to Port Washington WI; Wind Point WI to Winthrop Harbor IL; North Point Light to Wind Point WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued March 2 at 3:14PM CST until March 4 at 12:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 15 to 25 knots with gusts up to 30 knots
later Tuesday morning, veering west Tuesday afternoon and
lingering into Tuesday evening. Waves 1 to 2 feet Tuesday
morning, building to 2 to 3 feet Tuesday afternoon and evening.

* WHERE...Nearshore Waters from Sheboygan to Winthrop Harbor IL.

* WHEN...From 9 AM Tuesday to midnight CST Tuesday night.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM TUESDAY TO MIDNIGHT CST TUESDAY NIGHT
